										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Happy July!  Today&#8217;s image dump of awesome is of artworks by &#8220;<a href="http://haryarti.deviantart.com/">haryarti</a>&#8221; from Kazakhstan.  You can find more fantastic artwork at his <a href="http://haryarti.deviantart.com/gallery/" target="_blank">Deviant Art page</a>.  Enjoy!</p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://haryarti.deviantart.com/art/Heavy-Rain-300414584" target="_blank"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" alt="Heavy Rain" src="http://fc00.deviantart.net/fs71/f/2012/225/8/2/heavy_rain_by_haryarti-d4yuxdk.jpg" width="576" height="304" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://haryarti.deviantart.com/art/Road-to-Uberwald-2-259212362" target="_blank"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter" alt="Road to Uberwald_2" src="http://th07.deviantart.net/fs71/PRE/i/2011/264/0/7/road_to_uberwald_2_by_haryarti-d4abtje.png" width="557" height="372" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://haryarti.deviantart.com/art/Sunset-of-Empire-281422782" target="_blank"><img decoding="async" class="alignnone" style="margin-right:5px;" alt="Sunset of Empire" src="http://th09.deviantart.net/fs71/PRE/i/2012/025/5/8/sunset_of_empire_by_haryarti-d4njv7i.jpg" width="285" height="440" /></a><a href="http://haryarti.deviantart.com/art/Hunter-275372024" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone" style="margin-left:5px;" alt="Hunter" src="http://th08.deviantart.net/fs71/PRE/i/2012/230/b/0/hunter_by_haryarti-d4jy6ew.jpg" width="248" height="407" /></a></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" alt="Iron Island" src="http://th08.deviantart.net/fs71/PRE/f/2011/361/b/8/iron_island_by_haryarti-d4kdxzn.jpg" width="544" height="275" /></p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://haryarti.deviantart.com/art/Stream-DarkTown-333524563" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" alt="Steam DarkTown" src="http://th09.deviantart.net/fs70/PRE/i/2012/295/7/4/stream_darktown_by_haryarti-d5ikl77.jpg" width="575" height="360" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
<p style="text-align:center;">Are you an artist/photographer/sculptor who loves Steampunk as much as I do?   Would you like to see your work featured on this blog?  Or, do you know of someone else who&#8217;s work you adore?  Please leave a comment on this post with a link or two!   I&#8217;ll happily feature anything that I think will fit the style of my blog.  And even if I don&#8217;t feature it, please please leave your info in a comment anyway!  More art is always better than less.</p>
